Title: Knee-High
Description:
Tess and Voss are waiting for you at the end of the tunnel. Once you arrive, the three of you will open the south gate from the inside, and let our forces into the city.

Head through the tunnel to meet them. Take this torch, the way is infested with vermin. 

I'll ready our forces to storm the gate the moment it is opened.
ObjectivesText: Make your way through the secret tunnel in Aderic's Repose to Gilneas City.
